Registry<String,BayeuxClientDistribution>
public class BayeuxClientDistributionRegistry
extends Object
implements Registry<String,BayeuxClientDistribution>

An implementation of a Registry providing thread-safe String-based registration and retrieval of BayeuxClientDistribution instances.

Constructor Summary
BayeuxClientDistributionRegistry()
           
BayeuxClientDistributionRegistry(AgentConfiguration agentConfiguration)
          Instantiates a BayeuxClientDistributionRegistry ensuring that all known Topology which contain the agent identified by AgentConfiguration.getCometUrl() automatically results in a new BayeuxClientDistribution with BayeuxClientDistribution.includesLocal set to true, being registered via this instance's registry
